    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist, who aims to become a professional soccer player, sets out on a journey of training!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overcome various obstacles to become a professional soccer player!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Contents</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control the protagonist to kick the ball and overcome various obstacles as you aim for the goal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kicking isn't just about striking the ball—there are many different techniques.<br>It's important to master a variety of moves, such as deciding which foot to kick with, adding curve, and choosing whether to kick the ball high or low.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use these different techniques to reach the goal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the game progresses, the difficulty increases, making it harder to clear stages.<br>When you're stuck, try experimenting with different kinds of kicks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additionally, make use of the practice ball and the sliding feature, which allows you to quickly retry after failing, so you can keep challenging yourself!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay Video and Distribution Guidelines</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can publish and distribute gameplay videos without permission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Credit notation is not required.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The developer is not responsible for any damage caused by publishing and distributing gameplay videos of this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These guidelines are subject to change.</p>",
